title: Navigating the Fall Housing Market
description: Nancy Strong and Craig Brody of Douglas Elliman join Mansion Global managing editor Beckie Strum to discuss the fall housing market, how things might be shifting to benefit buyers and how they can take advantage of slightly less competition.
